<i># Happy birthday to you #</i>

00:48.173 --> 00:51.792
<i># Happy birthday to you #</i>

00:52.427 --> 00:57.297
<i># Happy birthday, dear Jed #</i>

00:57.391 --> 01:02.102
<i># Happy birthday to you #</i>

01:02.187 --> 01:04.804
Okay, now make a wish. Blow 'em out.

01:09.861 --> 01:11.978
- [ALL] Yay!
- All right!

01:12.072 --> 01:14.530
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.

01:14.616 --> 01:15.652
All right.

01:20.664 --> 01:22.747
[WOMAN] Drayton, where are your manners?

01:22.833 --> 01:24.574
Give the first piece to the thief.

01:31.341 --> 01:33.833
[MAN WHIMPERING, BREATHING HEAVILY]

01:38.640 --> 01:39.676
[GRUNTING]

01:39.766 --> 01:41.382
I didn't steal your fuckin' pigs!

01:41.685 --> 01:44.848
You callin' my son a liar? He saw
your grubby hands steal our property.

01:45.564 --> 01:47.681
[GRUNTING]

01:47.774 --> 01:49.857
[SPITTING]

01:49.943 --> 01:52.435
Why would I go anywhere near your dirty pigs?

01:52.696 --> 01:54.062
Or your filthy family?

01:54.406 --> 01:59.321
I swear, the whole world gonna find out
what kind of brood you raising here, Verna!

01:59.411 --> 02:00.777
Shut him up. I've had enough.

02:01.288 --> 02:03.826
- Ohh!
- Listen to me.

02:04.166 --> 02:06.579
No hillbilly's gonna ruin
my son's special night.

02:07.628 --> 02:08.994
[GRUNTING]

02:09.755 --> 02:10.961
You ready for your present?

02:14.468 --> 02:16.505
You know you're my special boy.

02:17.095 --> 02:19.178
[MAN] Come on, Jed. Here you go.

02:20.223 --> 02:22.715
- [ALL LAUGHING]
- [VERNA] Jed.

02:22.809 --> 02:24.016
[MAN 2] Yeah, this is it, Jed.

02:26.813 --> 02:30.973
Now remember, bad people like him,
they're trying to break our family apart.

02:31.526 --> 02:35.064
But we're not gonna let that happen, right?
Now go on, now. Pick it up.

02:35.781 --> 02:37.113
Jed, pick it up.

02:37.908 --> 02:39.649
- Jed.
- Jed.

02:40.160 --> 02:41.901
- Jed. Jed.
- [POUNDING TABLE]

02:41.995 --> 02:43.987
- [ALL CHANTING] Jed. Jed. Jed.
- [VERNA] Pick it up, Jed.

02:44.081 --> 02:48.075
Jed! Jed! Jed! Jed! Jed! Jed! Jed! Jed!

02:48.168 --> 02:49.830
[VERNA] Come on, now.
You know what you have to do.

02:50.796 --> 02:53.664
- That's right, Jed!
- [MAN] Get him, boy!

02:54.132 --> 02:55.839
- [CHANTING CONTINUES]
- Come on now, Jed.

02:56.510 --> 02:58.968
Jed! Jed! Jed! Jed! Jed!

02:59.054 --> 03:00.795
No! No!

03:00.889 --> 03:03.472
- [OLD MAN] Here you go.
- [MAN 2] Get him, son!

03:03.558 --> 03:05.094
[CAPTIVE MAN] No!

03:05.185 --> 03:07.427
Ohh. Ohh. Ohh. Ohh...

03:07.521 --> 03:09.057
[CHAINSAW MOTOR SPUTTERS]

03:09.147 --> 03:11.890
- [MOTOR STARTS]
- [SCREAMS] No!

03:11.983 --> 03:14.100
- No!
- [OLD MAN] You can do it!

03:14.194 --> 03:15.480
[TEENAGER CACKLING]

03:15.570 --> 03:17.653
- [MAN 1] Whoo!
- [CHAINSAW ROARING]

03:19.116 --> 03:21.324
No!

03:21.410 --> 03:24.369
No, please! No!

03:24.454 --> 03:27.197
- No!
- [CHANTING] Jed. Jed.

03:27.290 --> 03:30.328
- Jed! Jed! Jed!
- [SCREAMING]

03:30.836 --> 03:32.577
Jed, go. Go.

03:33.296 --> 03:34.207
[MAN 2] That's right, do it!

03:35.382 --> 03:37.248
Jed! Jed! Jed!

03:38.385 --> 03:39.546
No!

03:39.970 --> 03:40.881
[GRUNTS]

03:42.347 --> 03:43.258
[YELLS]

03:43.765 --> 03:46.098
Stop! Stop now!

03:46.184 --> 03:47.220
[YELLS]

03:47.310 --> 03:48.972
[CHAINSAW REVS]

03:49.062 --> 03:51.349
[SCREAMING]

03:56.403 --> 03:59.817
- [CHAINSAW MOTOR STOPS]
- [SCREAMING]

04:01.950 --> 04:04.408
Hey. You let us down, Jed.

04:04.870 --> 04:06.202
[GRUNTS]

04:06.288 --> 04:08.245
- [MAN SCREAMING]
- It's okay.

04:08.832 --> 04:10.289
Your family's always here for you.

04:10.751 --> 04:11.662
Remember that.

04:12.586 --> 04:13.622
- Okay.
- [GRUNTS]

04:27.559 --> 04:29.221
[CRICKETS CHIRPING]

04:37.319 --> 04:39.402
[ROCK MUSIC PLAYS ON RADIO]

04:39.488 --> 04:41.696
- You tryin' to make us crash?
- You want me to stop?

04:41.782 --> 04:43.023
Nah, I didn't say that.

04:45.869 --> 04:48.156
[CAR ACCELERATES]

04:50.582 --> 04:51.618
Look out!

04:51.708 --> 04:52.698
[TIRES SCREECHING]

04:56.421 --> 04:57.878
What the hell was that thing?

04:59.424 --> 05:00.335
Hey, Betty.

05:07.891 --> 05:08.802
What is it?

05:10.268 --> 05:11.179
I don't know.

05:14.940 --> 05:15.851
Well, let's go.

05:18.068 --> 05:18.979
[EXHALES]

05:19.194 --> 05:20.981
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

05:25.242 --> 05:26.198
What?

05:28.495 --> 05:29.451
[GASPS]

05:30.372 --> 05:31.863
[SHUDDERED BREATHS]

05:34.793 --> 05:35.704
It's just a kid!

05:38.088 --> 05:39.044
Let's go!

05:39.965 --> 05:40.876
We're gonna be late!

05:43.510 --> 05:44.500
Hey, there.

05:49.266 --> 05:50.097
You okay?

05:50.183 --> 05:52.220
[BREATHES HEAVILY]

05:56.648 --> 05:58.355
You shouldn't play in the road.

05:58.900 --> 06:00.186
[BOY] Help me! Please!

06:06.992 --> 06:08.733
Hey, Betty, where you goin'?
I didn't hit him!

06:09.411 --> 06:11.027
- There's something wrong!
- Betty!

06:11.121 --> 06:12.032
He needs help!

06:12.831 --> 06:13.912
Jesus Christ.

06:18.712 --> 06:20.453
Hey, little guy, you hear me?

06:22.674 --> 06:23.630
Let me help you!

06:28.263 --> 06:29.174
Hello?

06:36.021 --> 06:38.229
It's okay! You can come out!

06:39.983 --> 06:40.894
Betty!

06:44.905 --> 06:46.237
Betty, where'd you get off to?

07:04.674 --> 07:05.710
[HINGES CREAK]

07:24.319 --> 07:25.605
[CLATTERING]

07:38.333 --> 07:40.120
- [FLOORBOARD CREAKS]
- [OBJECT CLANKS]

07:44.965 --> 07:46.627
- Hello?
- [FLOORBOARD CREAKS]

07:51.179 --> 07:52.090
Come on.

07:53.431 --> 07:54.717
I won't touch you.

07:57.477 --> 07:58.638
I just want to help.

07:58.853 --> 07:59.764
[CLATTERING]

08:05.902 --> 08:06.813
Okay?

08:07.570 --> 08:08.401
[CRACKING]

08:08.488 --> 08:09.899
- [WOOD BREAKING]
- [SCREAMS]

08:09.990 --> 08:11.276
[BODY THUDS]

08:23.294 --> 08:25.456
[GASPING, GROANING]

08:27.757 --> 08:29.623
You done good, Jed.

08:30.301 --> 08:32.884
Looks like you can learn a little after all.

08:40.352 --> 08:42.094
[GASPING, WHIMPERING]

08:51.114 --> 08:52.980
[WINCH CLANKING]

09:01.249 --> 09:02.205
[GURGLING]

09:05.003 --> 09:07.871
Nubbins, go ahead. Learn him some more.

09:09.966 --> 09:13.050
[WHIMPERING, GURGLING]

09:20.977 --> 09:22.468
[BLOWS KISS]

09:22.854 --> 09:23.970
Show him.

09:28.193 --> 09:29.149
[SCREAMS]

09:30.111 --> 09:32.148
[SIREN WAILING]

09:35.116 --> 09:36.698
[CAR APPROACHES, ENGINE SHUTS OFF]

09:36.785 --> 09:37.741
- [CAR DOOR SLAMS]
- Where is she?

09:37.827 --> 09:38.738
[COP] Take it easy, Hal.

09:39.162 --> 09:40.323
- Let me through, goddamn it!
- Hold it! Hold it!

09:40.413 --> 09:42.200
Get off me! Get the fuck off me!

09:42.290 --> 09:43.201
We'll figure out what happened.

09:43.291 --> 09:45.408
- Easy there, Hal.
- That's my baby in there.

09:45.502 --> 09:46.413
[GRUNTS]

09:47.337 --> 09:48.248
Is she in there?

09:48.838 --> 09:50.045
Is my baby in there?

09:50.381 --> 09:51.713
Answer me, goddamn it!

09:52.175 --> 09:53.131
We got one of them.

09:54.052 --> 09:54.963
Ahh...

09:56.346 --> 09:57.803
[PANTING]

09:57.889 --> 09:58.879
[GROANS]

10:00.850 --> 10:02.591
[CRYING]

10:03.228 --> 10:04.969
I couldn't get to her on time. [SNIFFLES]

10:05.063 --> 10:06.850
I'm real sorry, sir. I swear to God.

10:09.275 --> 10:10.391
[HAL] Drayton Sawyer.

10:13.696 --> 10:15.437
This time it ain't the Gorman House.

10:15.532 --> 10:18.821
Nah. You're grown up now.

10:21.412 --> 10:23.028
That means the gas chamber for you.

10:23.248 --> 10:24.329
[CHUCKLES]

10:27.043 --> 10:28.033
For what?

10:28.503 --> 10:31.746
You arrestin' me for finding the body?
That ain't no crime I heard of.

10:32.382 --> 10:34.920
How about I put a bullet
right in your fuckin' skull, huh?

10:35.009 --> 10:35.999
- [COP 1] Hold on.
- [COP 2] Put it away, Hal.

10:36.094 --> 10:38.677
- Come on, now.
- He's right. We ain't got nothin' on him.

10:39.097 --> 10:41.134
[COP 1] Easy, Hal. Keep your head on.

10:41.224 --> 10:43.841
- [COP 2] Hal, he ain't worth it.
- [COP 3] Come on, Hal. Put the gun down.

10:43.935 --> 10:45.016
Fuckin' trash.

10:54.195 --> 10:55.606
[CHATTER OVER POLICE RADIO]

10:56.364 --> 10:58.230
You let those boys go this instant.

10:58.616 --> 11:00.107
Don't count on it, Verna.

11:01.327 --> 11:03.535
You see them do something wrong?
No. No. I didn't think so.

11:03.621 --> 11:05.487
You uncuff him! You let him out of the car!

11:06.082 --> 11:06.993
No.

11:07.500 --> 11:08.741
He's stayin' right there.

11:09.961 --> 11:10.872
What for?

11:11.379 --> 11:14.042
He's not under arrest. He's under protection.

11:14.382 --> 11:15.839
- From you.
- What are you talkin' about?

11:17.093 --> 11:19.585
I can't count how many
crime scenes I've been to

11:19.679 --> 11:22.137
where there just happened
to be Sawyers there already.

11:22.974 --> 11:25.341
- Them kids ain't safe with you.
- Horseshit.

11:26.686 --> 11:28.678
Send some units over to the Sawyer house.

11:29.314 --> 11:31.397
You round up all the minors.
I want all of them.

11:31.482 --> 11:33.098
- You hear me?
- You can't do that. You can't do that.

11:33.526 --> 11:36.610
Well, I'll have a warrant that says I can
by the time we arrive.

11:37.530 --> 11:39.112
It's called child endangerment.

11:40.909 --> 11:42.366
You take one of mine...

11:43.745 --> 11:45.611
and I'll take all yours, Verna.

11:52.337 --> 11:53.327
All of 'em.

11:58.134 --> 12:01.593
[MAN] <i>In 1935, the state of Texas instituted</i>

12:01.679 --> 12:04.137
<i>a endangered childcare program.</i>

12:04.474 --> 12:07.763
The first year, nearly 50 children
were taken from homes

12:07.852 --> 12:10.469
where criminal activity was the norm.

12:11.189 --> 12:14.023
Most of these children were given new names

12:14.108 --> 12:15.770
and entered into foster care.

12:15.860 --> 12:19.194
Others, the product of degenerate parentage,

12:19.781 --> 12:22.239
were remitted here to Gorman House.

12:23.534 --> 12:28.154
You'll take care of their psychological,
physical needs.

12:28.581 --> 12:29.537
Yes, sir.

12:29.916 --> 12:32.329
I've been wanting to
come on here for a long time.

12:32.669 --> 12:35.082
- I think I can help them.
- Elizabeth.

12:35.171 --> 12:37.037
Oh, please, sir. Lizzy's... Lizzy's fine.

12:37.131 --> 12:38.417
Elizabeth.

12:39.634 --> 12:44.174
Most of these kids will end up in prison
or mental institutions.

12:45.223 --> 12:48.432
Keeping them here is safer for everyone.

12:49.352 --> 12:50.513
Keep your guard up.

12:54.691 --> 12:56.353
[LOW CHATTER]

12:59.404 --> 13:01.111
- [DOOR CLOSES]
- [LOCK CLICKS]

13:03.032 --> 13:05.570
[MAN SINGING ON RADIO, INDISTINCT]

13:09.706 --> 13:12.323
[HUMMING MELODY]

13:18.381 --> 13:20.043
[BOOKS BANGING]

13:22.510 --> 13:23.842
[WOMAN GIGGLING]

13:25.221 --> 13:27.053
[WOMAN 2] Can I get some water?

13:28.099 --> 13:29.260
I'm thirsty.

13:35.481 --> 13:36.392
Well, hello.

13:37.734 --> 13:38.850
My name is Lizzy.

13:38.943 --> 13:41.777
I'm new here,
and I want to get to know y'all.

13:43.614 --> 13:44.695
[GRUNTS]

13:45.241 --> 13:47.574
Oh. That's Bud.

13:49.662 --> 13:51.619
You don't say all that much, do you, big guy?

13:53.249 --> 13:55.036
[MAN] Nuh-uh. Uh-uh.

13:55.418 --> 13:59.583
- Uh... You're in my seat.
- Oh. Sorry.

14:00.673 --> 14:02.039
Thank you kindly.

14:02.133 --> 14:03.374
- Uh, I'm...
- Lizzy.

14:03.468 --> 14:05.130
Yeah, I heard. I heard.

14:05.928 --> 14:07.635
Shit. Sorry. I'm Jackson.

14:08.890 --> 14:11.883
Jackson and Bud.

14:12.685 --> 14:14.893
And what meds we have you on, Jackson?

14:15.271 --> 14:16.387
Meds, huh?

14:17.732 --> 14:19.143
They give 'em to us and we take 'em, right?

14:19.233 --> 14:20.474
[LAUGHING]

14:20.985 --> 14:23.352
We figured you'd know more about
all of that than us, Lizzy.

14:24.697 --> 14:26.780
You aren't gonna be trouble for me, are you?

14:27.241 --> 14:28.857
No, not me, Lizzy.

14:30.161 --> 14:32.824
Is there a reason you keep
saying my name like that?

14:33.790 --> 14:37.625
No, uh... I reckon I might like
how it sounds, is all.

14:41.047 --> 14:42.663
- [LOUD SLAM]
- Fuck you, asshole!

14:42.757 --> 14:45.044
I'll pop your eyes
right the fuck out of your head!

14:45.843 --> 14:48.210
- Let him go.
- Mind your own business!

14:48.471 --> 14:50.929
Is it my business. What is the problem?

14:51.891 --> 14:53.848
He said some things I didn't care for.

14:54.685 --> 14:58.019
Something about a girl in a nurse uniform,
what she might taste like.

14:58.981 --> 15:01.974
Hey! Hey! Get off me! Let go!

15:03.069 --> 15:04.526
Fuck you, Frankenstein!

15:04.612 --> 15:05.819
Break it up, pinheads!

15:06.572 --> 15:08.734
- Back to what you were doing.
- I didn't do nothin'.

15:10.326 --> 15:11.237
[SOFTLY] I didn't do nothin'.

15:12.120 --> 15:13.031
Don't look at me.

15:22.672 --> 15:24.038
[SIGHS]

15:29.220 --> 15:30.256
[EXHALES]

15:46.070 --> 15:46.981
[SIGHS]

15:47.822 --> 15:49.654
- [WOMAN GROANS IN DISTANCE]
- [SCUFFLING]

15:53.703 --> 15:55.069
[SCUFFLING CONTINUES]

15:59.250 --> 16:00.491
[CLATTERING]

16:07.800 --> 16:08.916
- [YELPS]
- [GASPS]

16:09.385 --> 16:10.796
[WOMAN GRUNTING]

16:11.804 --> 16:13.796
[CHOKING]

16:14.140 --> 16:15.347
What-What are you doing?

16:15.975 --> 16:16.931
[COUGHING]

16:20.062 --> 16:20.973
Come here.

16:21.105 --> 16:23.188
[WHIMPERS, GRUNTS]

16:23.274 --> 16:25.015
[SCREAMING]

16:25.693 --> 16:26.854
What's the big deal?

16:26.944 --> 16:28.685
It was just a stupid mouse.

16:28.779 --> 16:30.111
[SQUEAKING]

16:31.782 --> 16:32.989
Got a light?

16:33.075 --> 16:34.532
You're not allowed to smoke in here.

16:35.786 --> 16:36.867
[CHUCKLES]

16:37.371 --> 16:39.203
I got me special permission.

16:40.458 --> 16:43.326
True story. You can ask Dr. Lang.

16:44.003 --> 16:46.290
- I will.
- He'll tell you it helps me.

16:47.632 --> 16:49.919
On account of my anxiety.

16:52.637 --> 16:54.879
[CHUCKLES] Truth is...

16:56.432 --> 16:58.219
it's 'cause I'm his favorite.

16:58.768 --> 17:00.179
He told me so.

17:00.269 --> 17:02.682
- You just got yourself a warnin'.
- For what?

17:02.772 --> 17:05.560
- I was takin' a bath.
- Get out.

17:09.612 --> 17:10.522
Bitch.

17:12.448 --> 17:13.939
Everything all right?

17:14.951 --> 17:17.489
Uh, yes, Dr. Lang. I'm... I'm fine.
[CLEARS THROAT]

17:17.744 --> 17:22.615
I'll have a word with Isaac and... Bud.

17:22.708 --> 17:24.290
No, Bud didn't do nothin'.

17:24.710 --> 17:27.248
Lookin' forward to our session
tomorrow, Jackson?

17:27.338 --> 17:30.627
Um, sir, he's right, actually.
Bud didn't do anything.

17:30.716 --> 17:32.833
He was just fighting?

17:33.678 --> 17:35.044
Well, he was protecting me.

17:35.137 --> 17:38.346
Remind me to tell you later
what he did to his last foster family.

17:38.432 --> 17:39.798
They took away his dog.

17:39.892 --> 17:41.383
[LANG SIGHS] Yes?

17:41.811 --> 17:46.101
That's a perfectly good reason
to bludgeon somebody into a coma?

17:46.691 --> 17:48.227
Yeah, well, I'm just sayin'.

18:20.433 --> 18:21.549
[GASPS]

18:21.642 --> 18:23.429
I'm sorry. I didn't mean to scare you.

18:24.729 --> 18:25.640
You didn't.

18:26.606 --> 18:27.972
Thanks for helping Bud.

18:29.191 --> 18:32.684
I know you don't even know him,
so that's, um... that's nice.

18:33.821 --> 18:35.312
Well, I'm here to help you all.

18:35.823 --> 18:36.734
So...

18:38.242 --> 18:40.279
You're the first nice one
we've had around here.

18:43.497 --> 18:44.954
So I thought you should know.

18:46.626 --> 18:47.537
Know what?

18:48.461 --> 18:50.498
What goes on in the ECT chamber.

18:51.672 --> 18:53.288
Kids around here got to callin' that

18:53.674 --> 18:55.882
"Dr. Lang's Chamber of Horrors."

18:56.719 --> 18:57.709
Piece of shit.

18:58.971 --> 18:59.882
Why is that?

19:00.431 --> 19:02.388
You drop by tonight,
you can find out for yourself.

19:04.435 --> 19:06.222
I think maybe you could even
do something about it.

19:08.147 --> 19:09.058
Yeah.

19:10.316 --> 19:11.227
Jackson.

19:13.986 --> 19:15.522
You're gonna get out of here someday.

19:16.364 --> 19:18.481
And just cause you can't
trust certain people...

19:20.368 --> 19:22.155
it doesn't mean you shouldn't trust others.

19:23.621 --> 19:25.078
Yeah, I'll think about that.

19:36.509 --> 19:37.966
I'm sorry to keep you waiting.

19:38.052 --> 19:40.635
Barry Farnsworth. We've been here an hour.

19:41.055 --> 19:42.045
Uh, we?

19:44.892 --> 19:46.178
[LANG] Miss Sawyer.

19:46.268 --> 19:48.430
[FARNSWORTH] It's Mrs. Carson now.

19:54.694 --> 19:55.901
I want to see Jed.

19:56.487 --> 19:58.570
We've been through this before.

19:59.115 --> 20:00.572
Year after year.

20:00.658 --> 20:01.569
He's my son.

20:02.284 --> 20:03.866
And I can afford me a lawyer now.

20:04.120 --> 20:05.736
This changes nothin'.

20:06.247 --> 20:09.331
He was taken from you for a reason.

20:10.167 --> 20:11.078
Show him.

20:12.044 --> 20:13.205
It's an injunction.

20:13.879 --> 20:17.418
Court says Mrs. Carson has
the right to visit.

20:25.349 --> 20:26.681
You have to let me see him.

20:28.102 --> 20:29.263
You bring me Jed.

20:30.354 --> 20:31.595
Well, that's a problem.

20:32.189 --> 20:34.556
Most of these kids are given a new name...

20:35.276 --> 20:38.144
so they can hide from their degenerate...

20:38.988 --> 20:40.479
criminal families.

20:41.574 --> 20:44.282
Jed probably wouldn't be able to recall you

20:44.368 --> 20:45.904
or even his real name.

20:45.995 --> 20:47.327
But you know who he is.

20:47.830 --> 20:49.287
You and that sideways ranger.

20:49.373 --> 20:50.454
You know 'em all.

20:50.541 --> 20:53.158
I have a lot of patients.

20:54.044 --> 20:56.878
We'll have to check the records
to be certain.

20:57.089 --> 20:58.500
That's bullshit. [SCOFFS]

20:58.591 --> 21:03.302
And that requires
an entirely different court order.

21:04.722 --> 21:06.930
The records are very sensitive.

21:07.975 --> 21:09.841
Get me the correct court order,

21:10.561 --> 21:13.304
I'll be happy to help you.

21:13.397 --> 21:15.480
Oh, that one took three months to get!

21:15.566 --> 21:17.432
Then I advise you to get on it quick!

21:17.526 --> 21:19.483
Jed is 18 soon.

21:19.987 --> 21:22.400
I'll recommend he be transferred to prison.

21:22.490 --> 21:23.571
You're a bastard.

21:25.659 --> 21:30.195
Even though you married into money
and hired yourself a snot-nose shyster,

21:31.081 --> 21:35.667
you are still hillbilly trash.

21:38.631 --> 21:39.747
[DOOR SLAMS]

21:42.426 --> 21:43.837
[FARNSWORTH]
I have a friend, a country clerk.

21:43.928 --> 21:45.260
Maybe he can push it through.

21:45.346 --> 21:47.008
- Don't matter! It's all bullshit!
- Whoa. Whoa.

21:47.097 --> 21:48.008
Lavatory.

21:48.098 --> 21:49.009
That way.

21:54.980 --> 21:57.097
[LOUD GRUNTING]

21:57.191 --> 21:59.854
[MAN] I warned you, Bud,
but you wouldn't listen.

22:02.905 --> 22:05.272
Come on. Man up, Bud.
This is for your own good.

22:11.372 --> 22:13.238
[BUD GRUNTING]

22:59.420 --> 23:01.707
[SHOUTING IN DISTANCE]

23:06.260 --> 23:08.172
[SHOUTING CONTINUES]

23:08.262 --> 23:09.503
[MAN] Calm down.

23:09.597 --> 23:11.634
[CONTINUES, INDISTINCT]

23:14.602 --> 23:16.810
Go get her. Office hours are over.

23:16.896 --> 23:19.388
I can't go into the ladies' room.

23:28.032 --> 23:29.148
[KNOCKING]

23:29.241 --> 23:31.198
- Ma'am?
- It's Mrs. Carson.

23:31.285 --> 23:32.275
[DOOR OPENS]

23:33.704 --> 23:35.286
Goddamn it. She's gone!

23:40.544 --> 23:43.753
[GRUNTS] Get... off me!

23:44.548 --> 23:45.584
Get out...

23:47.426 --> 23:48.883
[KEYS JINGLING]

23:50.220 --> 23:51.176
Jed, I'm coming!

23:51.764 --> 23:53.847
- [VERNA] Jed! Jed!
- [MAN] What was that?

23:54.516 --> 23:55.506
[VERNA] I'm here for you!

23:55.935 --> 23:57.517
[ALL MURMURING]

23:57.603 --> 23:59.310
- You hear me?
- [WOMAN] What is that?

23:59.396 --> 24:02.480
[BUD WHIMPERING]

24:02.566 --> 24:04.182
[LANG] You're next, Isaac.

24:07.738 --> 24:08.854
Are we ready?

24:09.114 --> 24:11.731
[BUD WHIMPERING]

24:11.825 --> 24:14.568
[EXCLAIMING, GAGGING]

24:15.204 --> 24:17.321
[WHIMPERING, CRYING]

24:17.748 --> 24:20.957
- [SWITCH CLICKS]
- [ELECTRICITY BUZZING]

24:21.043 --> 24:22.500
[BUD GROANING]

24:30.177 --> 24:31.634
[DIAL CLICKING]

24:39.144 --> 24:40.726
- [VERNA SHOUTING]
- [ALARM BELL RINGING]

24:40.813 --> 24:42.554
What the hell is that?

24:42.648 --> 24:44.560
[VERNA] Jed!

24:48.070 --> 24:50.733
- [RINGING CONTINUES]
- Jed! Jed!

24:50.823 --> 24:51.939
You can't be here!

24:54.076 --> 24:55.988
Damn that woman. I'll be back.

24:56.286 --> 24:57.197
[VERNA] Jed!

25:00.791 --> 25:02.032
- [INMATES SHOUTING]
- Jed!

25:03.168 --> 25:05.455
[SHOUTING CONTINUES]

25:09.591 --> 25:11.378
[RINGING CONTINUES]

25:11.468 --> 25:13.425
[LAUGHING, SHOUTING]

25:14.304 --> 25:15.260
[MAN] Come on!

25:32.322 --> 25:34.109
[WOMAN] Lizzy. Come quick.

25:34.533 --> 25:35.944
Kids are loose in the halls.

25:40.622 --> 25:42.454
[VERNA] Jed, I'm coming!

25:43.250 --> 25:44.957
Jed? Jed.

25:45.419 --> 25:47.251
Get your hands off me!

25:50.466 --> 25:51.377
Hey! [GRUNTS]

26:00.267 --> 26:01.178
[INDISTINCT]

26:02.895 --> 26:05.854
[FARNSWORTH]
My client was acting in self-defense.

26:05.939 --> 26:06.770
Get out.

26:06.857 --> 26:08.064
She was...

26:08.859 --> 26:11.146
[SHOUTING CONTINUES IN DISTANCE]

26:11.236 --> 26:12.602
[RINGING CONTINUES]

26:12.696 --> 26:15.234
That's it. Lock it down.

26:20.245 --> 26:21.281
[MAN] Whoo-hoo!

26:23.457 --> 26:24.664
[ALARM STOPS]

26:26.043 --> 26:27.204
[NURSE SCREAMING]

26:27.294 --> 26:28.956
[SHOUTING, SCREAMING]

26:30.672 --> 26:32.413
I can't believe you did that.

26:37.805 --> 26:39.637
[GASPING]

26:44.436 --> 26:45.722
[INMATES SHOUTING]

26:45.813 --> 26:48.226
[GLASS BREAKING]

26:58.283 --> 26:59.444
Want to give me a hand?

27:00.953 --> 27:02.660
[WOMAN] I saw you with him.

27:03.038 --> 27:08.534
And you know that Ike is my soulmate.

27:08.627 --> 27:10.994
[CHOKING]

27:12.548 --> 27:15.040
- [DOOR SLAMS OPEN]
- [INMATES SHOUTING]

27:19.847 --> 27:21.679
There's an emergency exit in the basement.

27:22.766 --> 27:24.007
Come on, follow me!

27:25.227 --> 27:28.470
I told you a thousand times
we're understaffed.

27:29.314 --> 27:30.725
Just get here before they...

27:30.816 --> 27:32.307
[BANGING]

27:32.734 --> 27:36.023
Uh... Just hurry.

27:36.864 --> 27:37.695
[HANGS UP PHONE]

27:37.781 --> 27:39.067
- [BANGING]
- Who's there?

27:43.954 --> 27:46.116
[BANGING CONTINUES]

28:00.804 --> 28:01.885
[GRUNTING]

28:01.972 --> 28:03.258
[OBJECT CLATTERS]

28:03.932 --> 28:05.139
Don't be stupid, Bud.

28:06.393 --> 28:07.349
Bud?

28:07.936 --> 28:09.302
They'll never let you go.

28:10.439 --> 28:12.271
Think about it, Bud!

28:26.455 --> 28:29.072
Let's get the fuck out of here, y'all!

28:31.376 --> 28:34.084
Ike, where you at? Ike!

28:36.882 --> 28:38.544
[LAUGHS]

28:40.427 --> 28:42.510
[SHRIEKING]

28:46.934 --> 28:48.516
[MOANING]

28:50.896 --> 28:52.012
[MOANING]

28:55.400 --> 28:56.982
[CACKLING]

29:01.949 --> 29:03.030
[MOANING]

29:06.161 --> 29:08.118
[MOANING]

29:12.459 --> 29:15.202
- [INMATES SHOUTING]
- [GLASS BREAKING]

29:15.545 --> 29:16.661
- Let's hide.
- Let's hide!

29:17.464 --> 29:18.375
Right here.

29:19.049 --> 29:20.711
[WHIMPERING]

29:27.349 --> 29:29.386
[NURSE SCREAMING]

29:43.073 --> 29:43.984
[SCREAMING STOPS]

29:52.165 --> 29:53.872
[JACKSON ROARING]

29:55.460 --> 29:56.701
[SCREAMS]

29:59.423 --> 30:01.210
[WHIMPERING]

30:07.055 --> 30:07.966
Come on.

30:13.895 --> 30:15.181
[IKE] Jackson's got a hostage.

30:15.272 --> 30:16.388
Hey, what's up?

30:17.107 --> 30:19.019
Hey, Doc has a nice ride.

30:19.735 --> 30:21.601
- Don't touch him!
- [LIZZY] Let go of me!

30:23.363 --> 30:24.228
Get going!

30:24.323 --> 30:25.689
- [IKE] Be quiet!
- [LIZZY] Let go!

30:27.284 --> 30:28.695
- [GROANS]
- You fuck!

30:29.745 --> 30:30.826
[LIZZY SCREAMS]

30:33.457 --> 30:34.288
[ROCK ON CAR RADIO]

30:34.374 --> 30:36.582
[IKE] They'll think twice about
shooting us down with her along.

30:36.668 --> 30:38.330
[WOMAN] Yes, they will!

30:38.837 --> 30:42.171
[WHOOPING, TRILLING, HOOTING]

30:42.716 --> 30:44.002
[SCREAMING]

30:45.302 --> 30:46.793
[WOMAN CACKLING]

30:46.887 --> 30:48.970
[SONG CONTINUES]

30:50.432 --> 30:51.297
[IKE] Hey.

30:51.391 --> 30:54.259
Hop in, stupid. I owe you one.

30:55.854 --> 30:58.141
[FEMALE SINGER]
<i># That's the day I walk away #</i>

30:58.231 --> 31:00.063
<i># A-walk-a-walk-a-walk-a-ooh #</i>

31:00.442 --> 31:03.310
[SONG CONTINUES, INDISTINCT]

31:03.403 --> 31:05.395
[WOMAN] Fuck you, Gorman!

31:29.679 --> 31:30.795
Well, don't you look nice?

31:32.974 --> 31:35.512
You just had to bring the prettiest nurse
along with us, didn't you?

31:35.602 --> 31:37.559
Oh... I didn't pick her.

31:38.355 --> 31:39.391
No, Jackson did.

31:40.232 --> 31:42.019
You got no reason to be jealous.

31:43.235 --> 31:46.273
Why'd I be jealous of someone
who's about to die?

31:47.114 --> 31:48.855
Everything at the proper time.

32:01.795 --> 32:02.876
[GRUNTS]

32:03.255 --> 32:04.245
Jackson!

32:05.257 --> 32:06.293
Oh, here we go.

32:06.967 --> 32:09.254
Hey, where do you think you're going, bitch?

32:09.886 --> 32:11.377
- [GRUNTS]
- [GROANS]

32:11.471 --> 32:12.678
Put me down, put me down.

32:12.973 --> 32:13.884
Fuck you!

32:16.935 --> 32:19.018
[WHIMPERING]

32:21.440 --> 32:22.806
[SCREAMING]

32:22.899 --> 32:25.107
Let go of me! Let go of me!

32:29.281 --> 32:32.900
Do that again,
I'll turn you into strawberry pie.

32:34.119 --> 32:37.283
I'm gonna kill him, I'm gonna kill him...

32:38.081 --> 32:39.663
right before your eyes.

32:42.586 --> 32:44.168
And that goes for you two, as well.

32:46.506 --> 32:50.466
Anyone bolts, and everyone dies.

32:50.552 --> 32:52.760
- You son of a bitch.
- [LIZZY] Jackson, wait.

32:53.930 --> 32:55.842
We're all gonna look out
for each other. It's okay.

33:02.022 --> 33:02.933
Change.

33:03.607 --> 33:05.940
No, you ain't makin' her get undressed.

33:06.401 --> 33:07.437
Oh, ain't I?

33:09.905 --> 33:10.941
You got clothes underneath?

33:13.783 --> 33:14.694
All right.

33:24.836 --> 33:26.202
Cut it out, you bastard...

33:26.838 --> 33:28.374
before I slit her throat.

33:29.090 --> 33:30.831
That ain't no way
to talk about our new friend.

33:32.135 --> 33:33.751
She's going with us all the way.

33:35.222 --> 33:36.463
Where are you takin' us?

33:36.556 --> 33:37.637
Mexico.

33:38.767 --> 33:39.928
Perhaps you've heard of it?

33:41.394 --> 33:43.181
Gonna find us some money,
find us some more wheels.

33:44.189 --> 33:47.148
Go past Austin, see my mom.
Y'all be... all be welcome there.

33:47.442 --> 33:48.728
My mama loves company.

33:51.363 --> 33:54.314
And soon as we get to the Mexican
border, we go our separate ways.

33:58.203 --> 34:00.286
Jackson, you got someplace
you want to get to?

34:01.581 --> 34:03.573
You got family somewhere?

34:04.417 --> 34:05.328
No.

34:06.336 --> 34:07.747
No, Mexico sounds like a plan.

34:22.101 --> 34:23.638
- [HAL] You Sorells?
- Yes, sir.

34:24.437 --> 34:25.393
Glad you could make it.

34:26.313 --> 34:28.054
- We know which one did this?
- No.

34:28.400 --> 34:29.311
We know who's missing.

34:29.859 --> 34:31.395
They're pulling up the files
for us right now.

34:31.735 --> 34:33.193
Bet I know who it was.

34:34.864 --> 34:37.197
This ain't the work of a confused child.

34:38.659 --> 34:39.571
This is evil.

34:40.996 --> 34:42.203
Needs puttin' down.

34:49.170 --> 34:50.126
They all mine?

34:52.007 --> 34:54.670
All but one were brought in by you, yeah.

34:58.888 --> 34:59.924
Roadblocks set?

35:00.599 --> 35:03.262
- Ten. Twenty miles out.
- Push 'em out more.

35:03.351 --> 35:06.344
I want every local cop
from here to New Mexico on the lookout.

35:07.188 --> 35:08.224
Yes, sir.

35:32.922 --> 35:34.834
[TELEPHONE RINGING]

35:39.512 --> 35:40.423
Hello.

35:42.349 --> 35:43.260
They're loose.

35:43.767 --> 35:44.678
Cops lookin'?

35:48.104 --> 35:49.470
Yeah, of course we'll pay ya.

35:49.856 --> 35:51.188
You just keep us updated.

35:52.275 --> 35:53.391
We're gonna find Jed.

35:57.113 --> 35:59.355
[CHATTER ON POLICE RADIO]

36:01.409 --> 36:03.992
[CAR MOVES PAST]

36:08.583 --> 36:10.370
- Lang's car was just spotted.
- Where?

36:10.752 --> 36:13.085
South on 385. I'll meet you there.

36:14.339 --> 36:15.250
Sorells.

36:16.466 --> 36:17.377
Yes, sir.

36:18.176 --> 36:19.917
Knowing these kids the way I do...

36:20.720 --> 36:22.256
they ain't givin' up easy.

36:23.264 --> 36:25.301
- I understand.
- I don't think you do.

36:26.309 --> 36:28.722
Just 'cause they're kids,
I don't want your men going soft.

36:29.187 --> 36:31.930
If they gotta shoot first
and let God sort it out...

36:32.023 --> 36:34.106
Well, that's permissible.

36:34.484 --> 36:35.440
You copy that?

36:36.319 --> 36:37.230
Copy.

36:40.240 --> 36:41.697
[ENGINE STARTS]

36:57.215 --> 36:58.456
[WOMAN] Fuck, I'm hungry.

36:58.550 --> 37:00.291
I thought the plan was not to be seen.

37:00.510 --> 37:02.502
People looking for a group with a mongoloid.

37:02.846 --> 37:03.882
We go in separate.

37:04.389 --> 37:07.097
- And you stays outside.
- [GRUNTS]

37:07.183 --> 37:09.516
You... stays quiet.

37:09.602 --> 37:12.094
- We have no money.
- Blah, blah, fuckin' blah.

37:12.188 --> 37:16.353
We improvise. There's food, there's money,
and there's cars to grab. Get in there.

37:18.319 --> 37:21.483
[ROCK AND ROLL PLAYS ON JUKEBOX]

37:21.573 --> 37:23.155
[IKE LAUGHING]

37:24.284 --> 37:25.616
Wanna see if I can throw it in your mouth?

37:25.702 --> 37:26.818
- Yeah.
- Okay.

37:27.871 --> 37:29.078
Oh, yeah.

37:29.164 --> 37:30.871
[LAUGHING]

37:32.250 --> 37:33.411
You all right, darlin'?

37:34.419 --> 37:35.375
Ma'am.

37:35.462 --> 37:36.873
You haven't touched your food.

37:38.548 --> 37:40.130
I'm just not hungry, I guess.

37:40.675 --> 37:41.631
I'll bag it up for you.

37:44.679 --> 37:45.590
Throw it in my mouth.

37:49.434 --> 37:52.268
- Aah!
- [BOTH LAUGH]

37:54.939 --> 37:56.271
What the fuck you lookin' at?

37:59.152 --> 38:00.939
Yeah, that's right, nothin'.

38:03.490 --> 38:04.776
Everybody think they can look down on us.

38:05.784 --> 38:06.740
It's not funny.

38:07.744 --> 38:08.609
You know...

38:08.703 --> 38:11.286
Why don't you, um, check to see
if he's got a gun?

38:19.464 --> 38:20.375
He's got a gun.

38:22.133 --> 38:24.250
- Let's start some shit up.
- Okay.

38:25.178 --> 38:26.510
I wish this was just normal.

38:28.890 --> 38:30.722
I wish we were just two people...

38:32.060 --> 38:33.471
here at a diner, you know.

38:35.980 --> 38:37.471
I wish I was somebody else.

38:44.239 --> 38:46.322
Sorry, y'all. That was my fault.

38:48.409 --> 38:49.820
[LAUGHS]

38:50.620 --> 38:52.077
Think it's time y'all clear out.

38:52.580 --> 38:53.866
Pay up and go.

38:54.457 --> 38:58.076
<i># We ain't got no money #</i>

39:01.673 --> 39:03.630
[SCREAMING]

39:04.968 --> 39:06.209
[MAN] Goddamn!

39:08.221 --> 39:09.587
Holy shit!

39:19.774 --> 39:21.356
Fuck, I love Texas.

39:23.361 --> 39:26.570
Everybody go ahead and put your keys
and cash on the edge of the table.

39:26.656 --> 39:27.772
Clarice, get a bag.

39:28.283 --> 39:30.275
Put your guns on the table, man!

39:30.785 --> 39:32.401
- Clarice?
- Coming.

39:32.871 --> 39:34.612
- Put your money on the table.
- [CLARICE] Are you all deaf?

39:34.706 --> 39:36.493
Get your fuckin' money out now!

39:37.500 --> 39:39.992
- [IKE] Get it on the table!
- Come on! We ain't got all day!

39:40.086 --> 39:41.167
[IKE] Fuck you!

39:41.713 --> 39:43.329
- [CLARICE] You!
- Let's move!

39:43.423 --> 39:44.504
- Give it up!
- No, wait!

39:45.925 --> 39:47.132
[IKE] Thank you!

39:47.760 --> 39:49.126
- Let's go!
- [GLASS SHATTERS]

39:51.764 --> 39:52.675
Fuck!

39:54.851 --> 39:56.308
- Ow!
- No.

39:56.394 --> 39:57.510
Where'd you go, bitch?

39:57.896 --> 40:00.183
- Get a hold of her!
- Stop it!

40:20.710 --> 40:21.951
[LIZZY] Let me go!

40:26.549 --> 40:28.711
- [LIZZY GASPS]
- [JACKSON] Go, go, go, go, go! Go!

40:29.719 --> 40:31.551
Come on! Come on! Go!

40:32.472 --> 40:33.508
[CLARICE] Get in!

40:48.446 --> 40:50.608
[SIREN WAILS, SLOWS]

40:54.327 --> 40:56.284
[CHATTERING]

41:17.600 --> 41:19.592
Yep, it were them.

41:20.937 --> 41:22.018
No doubt about it.

41:25.900 --> 41:26.811
What happened?

41:27.902 --> 41:29.484
They went buckshit crazy.

41:30.238 --> 41:31.604
Cuttin' up with the waitress.

41:32.198 --> 41:33.484
Then they started shootin'.

41:36.244 --> 41:37.530
You see which way they went?

41:37.912 --> 41:39.198
What car they took?

41:41.124 --> 41:42.660
Maybe they left in a wagon.

41:43.251 --> 41:45.618
- What color?
- Blue, I reckon.

41:46.713 --> 41:47.703
Or gray.

41:48.631 --> 41:49.587
A Ford.

41:51.592 --> 41:52.423
[JACKSON] Hey.

41:52.510 --> 41:54.843
Could have at least stolen a car
with a full tank of gas.

41:56.764 --> 41:59.848
[IKE] I don't look at the gas gauge
when someone's shooting me, asshole.

42:15.742 --> 42:16.858
[SHOTGUN COCKS]

42:35.928 --> 42:36.839
Quiet, now.

42:39.140 --> 42:40.130
Clarice, get over here.

42:42.769 --> 42:43.805
Get the door.

42:44.437 --> 42:45.518
Okay, on three, right?

42:45.605 --> 42:48.393
One, two, three.

42:52.945 --> 42:55.187
[SNIFFS] Smells like an old barn.

42:55.615 --> 42:56.651
You first, Lizzy.

42:57.742 --> 42:59.859
Well, go on and get in there.

43:00.286 --> 43:01.367
[CLARICE] Get the fuck in.

43:03.956 --> 43:04.992
Check it out, all right?

43:16.260 --> 43:17.876
[STUMBLES, GROANS]

43:21.557 --> 43:23.594
Well, it's as good a place
as any for the night.

43:24.727 --> 43:27.219
Can rest up, let the cops pass us up.

43:27.980 --> 43:30.142
Enjoy my mama's barbecue by dinnertime.

43:30.233 --> 43:31.724
[OBJECTS CLATTERING]

43:33.152 --> 43:35.314
[INSECTS BUZZING]

43:45.248 --> 43:47.114
[FLOORBOARDS CREAK]

43:48.668 --> 43:49.579
[GRUNTS]

43:51.170 --> 43:54.163
[WHIMPERING, SCREAMING]

44:00.346 --> 44:02.588
- [LAUGHS]
- Guess he died of loneliness.

44:09.397 --> 44:10.308
Sit down.

44:10.398 --> 44:11.434
[JACKSON] You're gonna be okay.

44:12.483 --> 44:13.439
Okay.

44:15.278 --> 44:17.235
I'm just gonna take a look, okay?

44:17.738 --> 44:19.195
You're gonna be okay, but I...

44:19.282 --> 44:21.239
I gotta put some pressure on it, okay?

44:21.826 --> 44:22.942
Moonshine.

44:23.703 --> 44:25.160
[LIZZY]
That's good, that's good, that's good.

44:25.913 --> 44:27.700
- [HYPERVENTILATING]
- Now breathe slow.

44:28.749 --> 44:31.332
- Come on, come on.
- That's good. That's good.

44:31.669 --> 44:33.535
[JACKSON] Squeeze. Make it better.

44:34.213 --> 44:36.045
Big arms like that and that's all you got?

44:36.549 --> 44:37.505
[LIZZY] That's good.

44:40.553 --> 44:42.761
We just gotta put some pressure on it. Okay?

44:48.477 --> 44:49.433
Jesus.

45:08.080 --> 45:09.571
Man, you're lucky I love you.

45:14.879 --> 45:15.790
Want some of this?

45:17.215 --> 45:18.126
All right.

45:19.800 --> 45:21.041
[GRUNTS]

45:24.847 --> 45:25.928
Make you feel better.

45:26.557 --> 45:29.049
Oh, God. Really?

45:29.435 --> 45:30.642
Yeah, why not?

45:31.270 --> 45:33.182
- What else are we gonna do?
- Yeah.

45:39.028 --> 45:39.859
Easy.

45:39.946 --> 45:41.812
- [COUGHS]
- Yeah.

45:49.497 --> 45:50.954
[CLARICE MOANING]

45:54.168 --> 45:56.785
[BOTH MOANING]

46:02.093 --> 46:03.504
[LAUGHING]

46:06.305 --> 46:07.386
[MOANING CONTINUES]

46:52.184 --> 46:54.176
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

47:02.695 --> 47:04.402
You're gonna aggravate your condition.

47:07.825 --> 47:08.941
My condition?

47:11.704 --> 47:13.195
What do you know about me?

47:15.458 --> 47:16.369
What now?

47:17.877 --> 47:19.493
You know she's seen our files.

47:20.421 --> 47:21.332
So?

47:22.298 --> 47:27.043
So, she knows where all those foster moms
who gave you shit live now.

47:27.762 --> 47:28.843
No, I don't.

47:30.056 --> 47:31.888
I only saw your medical charts. I swear.

47:32.308 --> 47:34.140
She's lying, Jackson.

47:34.643 --> 47:36.179
She says she doesn't know.

47:37.188 --> 47:38.554
Who cares if she saw anything?

47:39.482 --> 47:40.723
You don't want to find your family?

47:42.902 --> 47:44.518
[JACKSON] Bud's the only family I got.

47:46.489 --> 47:47.400
A real family.

47:49.575 --> 47:50.565
That's all I want.

47:50.659 --> 47:51.615
[CHUCKLES]

47:51.952 --> 47:54.069
I thought you said your family
were in Austin.

47:54.955 --> 47:56.412
They'd be thrilled to see you, you know.

47:56.499 --> 47:58.035
They keep fuckin' movin'.

47:58.584 --> 48:00.371
I swear, I don't know.

48:03.381 --> 48:04.997
Come on, man. Let's leave her be, huh?

48:05.800 --> 48:07.541
Oh, you sweet on her now?

48:09.804 --> 48:12.137
Fine, lover boy.

48:13.140 --> 48:14.051
Hey, uh...

48:14.725 --> 48:17.934
Good luck getting it up
with all the junk they got you on.

48:18.938 --> 48:20.304
Sleep tight, asshole.

48:22.983 --> 48:24.770
[JACKSON] Bud, you're on first watch.

48:25.152 --> 48:26.359
Get your ass out of bed.

48:41.669 --> 48:42.705
[CLATTERING]

48:51.011 --> 48:54.345
[ANIMAL CALLS, INDISTINCT]

48:55.808 --> 48:57.640
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]

49:52.781 --> 49:54.864
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

50:07.588 --> 50:09.625
[SCREAMING]

50:09.715 --> 50:12.207
- What'd I tell you about running away?
- Let go of me!

50:13.636 --> 50:16.253
[WHIMPERING, SCREAMING]

50:16.680 --> 50:18.296
Guess I'm just too intense.

50:18.390 --> 50:19.426
[CLOTH TEARING]

50:19.850 --> 50:21.512
I think for the benefit of folks sleeping...

50:21.936 --> 50:24.098
- best keep your mouth shut, huh?
- [MUFFLED SCREAM]

50:24.480 --> 50:25.436
[RAPID FOOTSTEPS APPROACH]

50:25.523 --> 50:26.730
[GRUNTS]

50:32.571 --> 50:34.312
[GRUNTING]

50:38.827 --> 50:39.817
Run!

50:49.380 --> 50:50.291
[GRUNTS]

50:55.719 --> 50:56.800
[SHOTGUN COCKS]

50:56.887 --> 50:59.004
What in the holy hell is going on here?

51:00.349 --> 51:01.260
[SPITS]

51:04.436 --> 51:05.392
[HUFFS]

51:08.232 --> 51:11.725
This little piggy's the worst goddamn
lookout in the Lone Star State.

51:13.237 --> 51:15.354
And this little piggy
just tried to abandon us all.

51:16.574 --> 51:18.110
Including his girlfriend here.

51:23.455 --> 51:25.993
Well, then maybe it's time we
get rid of all this dead weight.

51:29.253 --> 51:31.791
Calm down.
We got a plan and we're stickin' to it.

51:32.339 --> 51:33.830
Take these two back to the trailer, okay?

51:33.924 --> 51:34.960
Don't take your eyes off 'em.

51:35.301 --> 51:37.418
Bud, you're an idiot and a fool,

51:37.511 --> 51:38.968
and I don't know why God
bothered to make you.

51:39.054 --> 51:40.170
Now get away from me.

51:55.571 --> 51:56.482
Shit.

51:58.782 --> 52:00.318
[BELT BUCKLE CLATTERING]

52:02.911 --> 52:05.449
[URINATING]

52:14.715 --> 52:15.751
[TWIG SNAPS]

52:16.967 --> 52:18.924
[WIND WHISTLING]

52:32.441 --> 52:34.023
[URINATING STOPS]

52:37.655 --> 52:38.566
[ZIPPER CLOSES]

52:39.865 --> 52:40.946
[GRUNTS]

52:46.330 --> 52:48.492
[WHIMPERING]

52:59.760 --> 53:02.173
[WHIMPERING CONTINUES]

53:14.942 --> 53:16.729
[CRYING]

53:32.042 --> 53:33.249
[SKULL CRUNCHES]

53:34.837 --> 53:36.419
[BIRDS SINGING]

53:43.220 --> 53:44.131
[CLARICE] Where's Ike?

53:44.847 --> 53:45.758
Hey!

53:47.057 --> 53:48.013
Where's Ike?

53:50.269 --> 53:53.012
Maybe you should keep your voice down
in case somebody else is out there.

53:53.105 --> 53:55.313
And maybe you should kiss my Texan ass.

54:02.865 --> 54:03.776
Ike!

54:07.286 --> 54:08.276
Where's Bud?

54:09.037 --> 54:09.948
Oh, shit.

54:13.500 --> 54:14.411
Ike!

54:16.837 --> 54:18.203
Ike!

54:19.882 --> 54:21.464
- Okay. Come on.
- Ike?

54:22.217 --> 54:23.924
Jackson! This is our chance. Let's run.

54:24.011 --> 54:25.593
If she finds Bud, she's gonna kill him.

54:25.679 --> 54:27.261
Bud can take care of himself.

54:42.321 --> 54:43.937
Ike, where you at?

54:44.031 --> 54:45.192
[ECHOING]

54:55.542 --> 54:56.578
Oh! Stop!

54:56.668 --> 54:57.829
[PANTING] What?

54:59.963 --> 55:01.044
You don't want to see it.

55:07.429 --> 55:08.590
Bud, you okay?

55:16.230 --> 55:17.141
Hey.

55:17.731 --> 55:19.097
What did you do, big guy?

55:19.983 --> 55:21.099
Come on. Let's get you up.

55:21.568 --> 55:22.479
Come on.

55:23.028 --> 55:24.064
I got ya.

55:24.154 --> 55:25.110
Let me get a look at you.

55:27.241 --> 55:28.152
Let's go.

55:45.759 --> 55:47.716
Ike, where you at?

55:50.305 --> 55:51.216
Ike?

55:53.559 --> 55:54.720
[PISTOL COCKS]

55:55.435 --> 55:57.848
Nope. Hands up, darlin'.

55:58.689 --> 55:59.679
It's over.

56:01.441 --> 56:02.352
I got one!

56:04.403 --> 56:05.314
Drop the gun.

56:07.239 --> 56:08.229
I said drop it.

56:10.784 --> 56:12.070
All right, now turn around.

56:17.749 --> 56:18.865
Where are the others at?

56:19.376 --> 56:21.914
What do you mean, the others?
It's just me and Ike.

56:22.588 --> 56:23.920
And I can't find him.

56:26.174 --> 56:28.374
Just tell me where the others are,
and you'll be safe and sound.

56:28.468 --> 56:29.379
[HAL] What do we got?

56:32.681 --> 56:34.047
Fuckin' Hartman.

56:34.725 --> 56:37.638
He won't ask but once.
Just tell me where they are.

56:37.728 --> 56:38.844
What'd she say?

56:40.272 --> 56:42.980
That it's just her and Isaac.
She don't know where he is.

56:43.066 --> 56:44.807
Nothin' but bullshit then, huh?

56:47.487 --> 56:48.944
Good to see ya again, Clarice.

56:50.449 --> 56:51.610
[SCREAMS]

56:52.284 --> 56:54.776
Jesus Christ, Hartman! You coulda killed her.

56:54.870 --> 56:57.829
Get everybody to spread out. They're close.

56:58.749 --> 56:59.956
Dogs are on the way.

57:00.042 --> 57:02.159
All right, fan out! Wide circle.

57:02.461 --> 57:04.123
They're somewhere close by, okay?

57:04.630 --> 57:05.666
Don't!

57:06.715 --> 57:08.331
[LAUGHS]

57:09.343 --> 57:10.675
Yeah, you laugh it up, girl.

57:11.345 --> 57:12.802
Let's see how funny this gets, huh?

57:13.972 --> 57:16.259
- Feel that? Huh?
- [MOANS]

57:16.350 --> 57:17.261
Hey.

57:18.518 --> 57:21.056
This is your last chance, baby,
to tell me what I want to know.

57:21.813 --> 57:24.100
- [SCREAMING]
- Huh?

57:24.191 --> 57:25.272
[CLARICE] Don't!

57:25.651 --> 57:27.768
Where. They. At?

57:28.111 --> 57:29.022
[SPITS]

57:32.824 --> 57:33.735
[CHUCKLES]

57:37.663 --> 57:39.746
[CLARICE] Cops! Cops!

57:39.831 --> 57:41.197
Fuckin' cops!

57:44.503 --> 57:45.960
Fuckin' cops!

57:47.547 --> 57:49.004
- [GUNSHOT]
- [CLARICE SCREAMS]

57:49.091 --> 57:51.424
Shit. Hide! Go. Go, go. Go on.

57:56.598 --> 57:57.930
[JACKSON] Holy fuck.

57:58.016 --> 57:58.927
Who is he?

57:59.017 --> 58:01.725
Rounds up kids like us. Bad news.

58:05.190 --> 58:06.681
[WHIMPERS]

58:07.359 --> 58:08.349
[SCREAMS]

58:08.443 --> 58:09.399
He's a policeman.

58:09.486 --> 58:11.193
Yeah, a policeman that broke my nose once.

58:11.279 --> 58:12.736
- He can help us.
- He's a corrupt son of a bitch

58:12.823 --> 58:14.439
who has it out for kids
that get into trouble.

58:14.866 --> 58:16.698
He filled Gorman House
almost single-handedly.

58:18.870 --> 58:20.327
- [WHIMPERS]
- Get. Come on.

58:29.006 --> 58:30.918
- Get down there.
- [GRUNTS]

58:31.466 --> 58:32.377
Come on out!

58:33.760 --> 58:35.251
Y'all got nowhere to go!

58:36.138 --> 58:37.254
[LAUGHING]

58:42.227 --> 58:43.684
You want to let me in on the joke?

58:43.979 --> 58:45.436
Fuck you, pig.

58:46.148 --> 58:48.640
You're the fuckin' joke. You ain't shit.

58:49.776 --> 58:51.108
I said come out!

58:54.656 --> 58:56.192
Your friends got guns in there?

58:56.867 --> 58:58.074
You ain't law.

58:58.744 --> 59:00.656
You're just a sad old man...

59:02.122 --> 59:05.035
cryin' over his stupid, dead little girl.

59:07.210 --> 59:08.951
- [MAN GASPS]
- [LIZZY] Oh, no!

59:09.755 --> 59:11.838
If you go, me and Bud will be next.

59:11.923 --> 59:13.289
[SORELLS] Holy shit, Hartman!

59:15.510 --> 59:18.173
Jesus fuck, Hartman! You out of your mind?

59:18.680 --> 59:20.546
You forget what these fuckin' kids
did at the diner?

59:21.308 --> 59:22.719
It's called justice, boy.

59:29.316 --> 59:30.648
Shh.

59:30.734 --> 59:32.270
Get off me!

59:47.167 --> 59:48.078
Get in there.

59:59.179 --> 01:00:00.090
What do you got?

01:00:00.597 --> 01:00:01.587
We got a body.

01:00:01.681 --> 01:00:02.797
It's not one of them.

01:00:04.101 --> 01:00:05.217
It's been in there a while.

01:00:05.977 --> 01:00:06.888
Let's move out.

01:00:08.647 --> 01:00:09.728
They gotta be close.

01:00:18.281 --> 01:00:19.192
Lizzy!

01:00:20.283 --> 01:00:21.819
- Hey!
- [INSECTS BUZZING]

01:00:21.910 --> 01:00:23.071
Ohh. [GROANS]

01:00:26.748 --> 01:00:28.034
- [DOGS BARKING]
- [HARTMAN] Fan out!

01:00:28.125 --> 01:00:29.241
Shit. Dogs.

01:00:30.710 --> 01:00:32.042
[COP] She got something. Over here!

01:00:32.129 --> 01:00:33.620
[BARKING CONTINUES]

01:00:33.713 --> 01:00:34.624
Get a whiff here!

01:00:41.680 --> 01:00:43.797
Oh, it's nothin'. Head over the ridge.

01:00:48.103 --> 01:00:49.594
[COP SHOUTING]

01:01:05.287 --> 01:01:07.119
[LIZZY GASPING]

01:01:13.545 --> 01:01:15.457
[GRUNTING]

01:01:29.519 --> 01:01:30.726
[GRUNTS]

01:01:41.281 --> 01:01:42.488
[WHIMPERS]

01:01:58.340 --> 01:01:59.831
[GULPING]

01:02:03.261 --> 01:02:04.672
[COUGHING]

01:02:30.538 --> 01:02:31.824
[SPITS]

01:02:44.427 --> 01:02:45.838
[VEHICLE PASSING]

01:02:47.639 --> 01:02:49.471
Hey! Hey!

01:02:49.975 --> 01:02:52.137
Stop! Please stop!

01:02:52.477 --> 01:02:53.934
[TIRES SCREECH]

01:02:54.020 --> 01:02:54.931
Stop!

01:02:58.608 --> 01:03:01.976
Dispatch. I got three suspects
at the old bridge.

01:03:03.321 --> 01:03:05.278
[WOMAN] <i>Copy that. Backup is on the way.</i>

01:03:08.159 --> 01:03:09.491
Don't you fuckin' move!

01:03:13.790 --> 01:03:15.497
[COP] Get back! Stay back!

01:03:17.043 --> 01:03:18.784
No!

01:03:28.888 --> 01:03:30.129
[GRUNTS]

01:03:33.018 --> 01:03:34.930
[YELLS]

01:03:35.937 --> 01:03:37.394
[YELLS]

01:03:42.902 --> 01:03:45.940
[YELLING]

01:03:47.157 --> 01:03:48.568
Stop! Stop it!

01:03:48.658 --> 01:03:50.149
[SCREAMS]

01:03:52.370 --> 01:03:55.829
- [ROARS]
- [ENGINE STARTS]

01:04:05.258 --> 01:04:07.215
Fuck! They killed Bud! Fuck!

01:04:07.302 --> 01:04:08.543
Fuck, fuck, fuck!

01:04:08.636 --> 01:04:10.753
Fuck! Fuck!

01:04:10.847 --> 01:04:11.758
Fuck!

01:04:11.848 --> 01:04:14.807
Why'd you run away?
Why the fuck did you run away?

01:04:14.893 --> 01:04:17.476
You're insane. You just killed that cop.

01:04:17.562 --> 01:04:20.054
You got Bud killed!
You got Bud fucking killed!

01:04:20.148 --> 01:04:22.231
Fuck! Fuck!

01:04:22.525 --> 01:04:25.609
You're just like everybody else.
You fuckin' liar.

01:04:25.695 --> 01:04:27.357
Why'd I think you'd be any different?

01:04:28.531 --> 01:04:29.521
Fuck!

01:04:29.783 --> 01:04:31.024
- [GUNSHOT]
- [YELPS]

01:04:35.288 --> 01:04:37.280
It's Hartman! Drive! Drive!

01:04:37.374 --> 01:04:39.161
[GUNFIRE CONTINUES]

01:04:39.667 --> 01:04:40.908
[LIZZY SCREAMS]

01:04:41.336 --> 01:04:42.668
[TIRES SCREECH]

01:04:45.840 --> 01:04:46.796
[TIRES SCREECH]

01:04:47.258 --> 01:04:48.715
[GASPS, WHIMPERS]

01:04:52.680 --> 01:04:53.921
[GROANING]

01:05:02.565 --> 01:05:03.726
- [GUNFIRE CONTINUES]
- [YELPS]

01:05:03.817 --> 01:05:05.308
[TIRES SCREECH]

01:05:18.456 --> 01:05:20.288
[STATIC ON POLICE RADIO]

01:05:21.209 --> 01:05:22.325
[SORELLS] <i>Hartman?</i>

01:05:23.086 --> 01:05:24.577
<i>Come in, Hartman. You there?</i>

01:05:25.880 --> 01:05:26.711
<i>Hartman?</i>

01:05:27.257 --> 01:05:28.748
- [THUNDERCLAP]
- [RAIN FALLING]

01:05:31.344 --> 01:05:32.926
[GASPS, GRUNTS]

01:05:42.814 --> 01:05:43.930
<i>Hartman, come in.</i>

01:05:44.441 --> 01:05:45.977
<i>It's Sorells. You there?</i>

01:05:48.820 --> 01:05:49.810
<i>Hartman?</i>

01:05:50.530 --> 01:05:51.646
<i>Hartman, come in.</i>

01:05:52.282 --> 01:05:54.194
[GRUNTING, WHIMPERING]

01:06:02.417 --> 01:06:03.328
Hello?

01:06:04.294 --> 01:06:05.830
My name is Elizabeth White.

01:06:08.173 --> 01:06:10.631
I was kidnapped from Gorman House
and held hostage.

01:06:12.135 --> 01:06:13.091
<i>Elizabeth?</i>

01:06:13.595 --> 01:06:15.678
This is Trooper Sorells, Texas State Police.

01:06:16.514 --> 01:06:17.470
Where you at, girl?

01:06:18.850 --> 01:06:19.806
I don't know.

01:06:20.852 --> 01:06:21.808
Uh...

01:06:21.895 --> 01:06:23.807
I'm locked in the back of a police car.

01:06:24.898 --> 01:06:26.230
Why don't you go on, tell me what you see?

01:06:26.524 --> 01:06:27.560
<i>An old barn.</i>

01:06:28.651 --> 01:06:30.142
Looks like it might collapse.

01:06:31.362 --> 01:06:33.570
<i>All right. Okay. You stay put, darlin', yeah?</i>

01:06:33.990 --> 01:06:35.322
Dispatch, I'm on it.

01:06:41.956 --> 01:06:43.663
[SCREAMING]

01:06:48.046 --> 01:06:49.332
[SCREAMING CONTINUES]

01:06:54.719 --> 01:06:55.880
Get down there.

01:07:00.725 --> 01:07:01.681
[LIZZY] Jackson?

01:07:02.018 --> 01:07:03.350
There is no Jackson, honey.

01:07:03.811 --> 01:07:06.770
It's Jed. Jedidiah Sawyer.

01:07:09.943 --> 01:07:11.309
What are you doing to him?

01:07:12.403 --> 01:07:13.735
I'm settin' things right.

01:07:17.659 --> 01:07:18.900
You know where he started?

01:07:22.038 --> 01:07:23.245
Killin' my little girl.

01:07:24.290 --> 01:07:25.201
Right here.

01:07:26.209 --> 01:07:27.325
Please let me go.

01:07:29.796 --> 01:07:31.128
You ain't goin' nowhere.

01:07:35.009 --> 01:07:36.341
This shit's about to get fun.

01:07:54.112 --> 01:07:55.353
[MAN] What do you want?

01:07:55.572 --> 01:07:58.690
- Where's Verna?
- Other side of town. Carson estate.

01:07:58.783 --> 01:07:59.864
She's not there.

01:08:01.327 --> 01:08:02.659
Look, it's about Jed.

01:08:04.247 --> 01:08:05.613
[OBJECTS CLATTERING]

01:08:06.291 --> 01:08:08.624
Pig is here. Says it's about Jed.

01:08:19.470 --> 01:08:20.426
What is it?

01:08:21.264 --> 01:08:22.505
Hartman's got your boy.

01:08:23.640 --> 01:08:25.348
Holed up in an old barn somewhere.

01:08:26.394 --> 01:08:28.055
- Sound familiar?
- Sound right.

01:08:28.145 --> 01:08:30.638
Hey. What about me?

01:08:31.441 --> 01:08:32.352
What about you?

01:08:33.401 --> 01:08:34.937
I thought we had an arrangement.

01:08:36.362 --> 01:08:38.979
You know? Some kind of understanding?

01:08:45.287 --> 01:08:46.323
That we did.

01:08:47.790 --> 01:08:49.031
[THUNDERCLAP]

01:08:57.884 --> 01:08:58.965
- [STABBING]
- [SORELLS GASPS]

01:09:03.430 --> 01:09:05.046
[GRUNTS, GASPS]

01:09:06.267 --> 01:09:07.178
Pig.

01:09:10.104 --> 01:09:11.015
[SORELLS, WEAKLY] No.

01:09:11.939 --> 01:09:13.895
No. No, no.

01:09:15.193 --> 01:09:18.185
No. No! [GASPS]

01:09:18.279 --> 01:09:19.941
[COUGHING]

01:09:21.240 --> 01:09:23.232
[PIGS GRUNTING]

01:09:24.452 --> 01:09:26.068
[SQUEALING]

01:09:28.747 --> 01:09:30.363
[SCREAMING]

01:09:30.457 --> 01:09:31.493
Let's go get Jed.

01:09:32.042 --> 01:09:33.500
He's at the old barn.

01:09:33.920 --> 01:09:35.877
- [SCREAMING CONTINUES]
- You sure he's gonna remember us?

