01:13:19.896 --> 01:13:21.387
[COUGHS, SNIFFLES]

01:13:28.487 --> 01:13:29.648
[GRUNTS]

01:13:40.082 --> 01:13:41.163
[GRUNTS]

01:13:42.585 --> 01:13:43.541
[HARTMAN] Elizabeth.

01:13:43.794 --> 01:13:46.207
[THUNDER RUMBLING]

01:13:46.297 --> 01:13:47.413
Elizabeth.

01:13:50.092 --> 01:13:52.425
